        "text": "Talia Bregman has a management-side employment law practice. She advises both federally and provincially regulated employers on all aspects of employment law from drafting employment contracts and workplace policies to negotiating termination packages and workforce reductions. Talia also provides advice on labour and employment related aspects of corporate transactions.\n\nTalia summered and articled with the firm before becoming an associate. She is a member of the Canadian Bar Association and the Ontario Bar Association and is also a registered notary public."
